room_title: Escape room "Get back on Santa's Good List" by Code To Escape in Daytona Beach
room_address: 119 S Palmetto Ave Daytona Beach, FL 32114
room_description: Once upon a time the sky was dark, the clouds were high, and air traffic was normal. The Air Police report claims Santa was riding his sleigh from the North whilst Aladdin was cross his way from the East. Aladdin was checking his messages and hit Santa's sleigh. Luckily there were no injuries. Unfortunately the oil from Aladdin Magic Lamp spilled onto Santa's Good List and it caught fire. Here is your chance to fill Santa's Good List! You have 30 minutes to find the replacement book and sneak your name into it to get some extra presents for Christmas.
